div.p: Created: Initialize saga context, validate definition
Running: Execute forward steps, track progress, handle dependencies
Compensating: Execute compensation steps in reverse order
Completed: Clean up resources, notify subscribers
Failed: Log errors, alert monitoring, preserve state for analysis

• Definition Submitted: New saga registered • Start Execution: Begin forward step execution
• Step Success/Failure: Individual step outcomes • Timeout: Step or saga-level timeouts • Compensation Complete: All rollback steps finished
